dct_title_s: Mapa referente ao indicado canal São Francisco-Jaguaribe
dct_description_sm: organizado pelo enjenheiro Roberto Miller ... sob a direção do chefe topógrafo Guilherme Lane.
Relief shown by shading and spot heights.
Covers parts of Ceará, Pernambuco, and Bahía states.
Includes graph showing river elevations along cities (horizontal scale 1:4,000,000, vertical 1:4,000) with river legend.
Map shows waterways, islands, roads, railroads, state lines.
